OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day with plenty of warm
OL,7,Fsunshine. Dry overnight but turning
OL,8,Fmurky in the far southwest of Cornwall
OL,9,Fwith the odd spot of rain. The low
OL,10,Fchance of a thundery downpour in the
OL,11,Fsouth. Mild overnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA murky morning in the far
OL,14,Fsouthwest, elsewhere dry with bright
OL,15,Fhazy sunshine but low cloud lingering
OL,16,Falong the coasts. Risk of the odd
OL,17,Fshower. Warm in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
