OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FSpells
OL,6,Fof rain possible at times over the
OL,7,Fnext few days, with low cloud along
OL,8,Fcoasts, mixed with drier and brighter
OL,9,Fintervals. Turning more humid,
OL,10,Fespecially overnight.
